{"title":"永远、永远挽紧友爱的臂膀（歌词）","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远、永远挽紧友爱的臂膀（歌词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌拉尔的炼钢工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把红色的信笺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄到南方的鞍钢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉门油矿的矿工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把第一瓶原油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到巴库的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在莫斯科的飞机场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常有中国人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来作亲切的拜访；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京的火车站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常有苏联的贵宾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含着友好的微笑来往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"克里姆林宫的红星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了长江边的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔船、田野和村庄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上的灯盏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也给伏尔加河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送去了温暖的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"副歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们的喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是苏联人民的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！苏联的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我们每一个人的期望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，我们，六万万的我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远和苏联人民挽紧臂膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远，永远挽紧友爱的臂膀"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}